map_ids_uniprot

map_ids_uniprot.Rd

Access to uniprot web API. For more detail see https://www.uniprot.org/help/uploadlists

map_ids_uniprot(
  data,
  ID_col = "UniprotID",
  from = "ACC+ID",
  to = "P_ENTREZGENEID",
  format = "tab"
)

Arguments

data

data
ID_col

column name containing id's
from

id type
to

id type
format

in which format to return the mapping
